x=\"2\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Avis 3\"></span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h1 class=\"elxR-title\">Rasoir Électrique Précision</h1>\n  <hr class=\"elxR-hr\">\n\n  <ul class=\"elxR-bullets\">\n    <li>✔ <strong>Rasage doux</strong> : évite irritations & coupures</li>\n    <li>✔ <strong>Zones sensibles</strong> : bikini, aisselles, corps</li>\n    <li>✔ <strong>Peau plus nette</strong> : aide à prévenir les poils incarnés</li>\n  </ul>\n\n</section>\n\n<script>\n(function(){\n  const section = document.querySelector('[data-elx-reviews]');\n  if(!section) return;\n\n  const quoteEl = section.querySelector('[data-elx-quote]');\n  const metaEl  = section.querySelector('[data-elx-meta]');\n  const avatarEl = section.querySelector('[data-elx-avatar]');\n  const dots = section.querySelectorAll('.elxR-dot');\n\n  const slides = [\n    {quote:\"Zéro irritation, hyper doux. Je recommande à 100%.\", name:\"Claire M.\", city:\"Paris\", days:6, avatar:\"https://i.pravatar.cc/84?img=15\"},\n    {quote:\"Super précis sur les zones sensibles.\", name:\"Sophie L.\", city:\"Lyon\", days:12, avatar:\"https://i.pravatar.cc/84?img=28\"},\n    {quote:\"Peau nette et moins de poils incarnés.\", name:\"Émilie R.\", city:\"Nice\", days:3, avatar:\"https://i.pravatar.cc/84?img=45\"}\n  ];\n\n  let current = 0;\n\n  function render(i){\n    const s = slides[i];\n    quoteEl.textContent = s.quote;\n    avatarEl.src = s.avatar;\n    metaEl.textContent = `${s.name} · ${s.city} · il y a ${s.days} jours`;\n    dots.forEach((d,idx)=>d.classList.toggle(\"active\", idx===i));\n    current = i;\n  }\n\n  function goTo(idx){\n    const i = Number(idx);\n    if(Number.isNaN(i)) return;\n    render(i);\n  }\n\n  dots.forEach(dot=>{\n    dot.addEventListener(\"click\",()=> goTo(dot.dataset.idx));\n    dot.addEventListener(\"keydown\",(e)=>{\n      if(e.key === \"Enter\" || e.key === \" \"){\n        e.preventDefault();\n        goTo(dot.dataset.idx);\n      }\n    });\n  });\n\n  setInterval(()=>{ render((current+1)%slides.length); }, 3500);\n  render(0);\n})();\n</script>"
